Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.25,0:00:17.42,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,M-Move, arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.42,0:00:19.67,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Hamon will fill my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.67,0:00:23.62,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do something\Nbefore that happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.50,0:00:42.06,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.29,0:00:45.63,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We'll find you a new body.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.59,0:00:57.83,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,An excerpt from the December 4, 1888\Nedition of The London Press:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.21,0:01:07.30,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"73 of the 452 people living in Wind\NKnights Lot went missing overnight."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.30,0:01:12.30,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"Investigators have one lead\Nbased on witness accounts."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.65,0:01:18.68,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"Four outsiders were seen burning\Na man's clothing at the cliff's base."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.21,0:01:25.77,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"One of them was seen smashing\Na curious stone mask with a hammer."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.00,0:01:28.75,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Our work is done!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.10,0:01:44.54,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Two stars fallen from the heavens
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.34,0:01:51.97,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Swallowed by waters swirling\Nlight and dark
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:56.84,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Their ripples move outward,\Npulled toward each other
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.87,0:02:08.43,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sun will guide the man\Nwho walks the path of honor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.43,0:02:14.11,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And for the man who follows\Nhis ambition...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.46,0:02:15.84,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...a sacrifice awaits
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:26.50,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With pounding heart\Nand burning will
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:30.03,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With thundering fists
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.03,0:02:33.50,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And overflowing bravery
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:39.58,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He steps forward, free of doubt
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:43.75,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A fate determined by his blood
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:47.63,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:04.52,Type,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chapter 9: The Last Hamon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.96,0:03:05.67,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Joestar heir Jonathan Joestar weds
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.67,0:03:09.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\NErina, only daughter of the Pendletons!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:14.17,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They plan to spend their\Nhoneymoon in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:16.50,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:18.21,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:20.88,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They're about to depart!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:27.05,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:29.35,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Mr. Speedwagon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:32.02,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You almost missed seeing them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:35.34,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late.\NSo where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:36.89,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They're on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:39.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's about to set sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:41.77,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:43.66,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where can I see them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:46.03,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Father STYX...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:49.79,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...we expect much\Nfrom your mission to Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:52.78,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do what I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.52,0:03:57.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:03:58.50,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Gangway!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.66,0:04:01.38,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What weighs so much in this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:06.25,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?\NSome weird Asian told me to move it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:15.28,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Did you guys hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.28,0:04:17.40,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Quit flapping your gums and move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.81,0:04:20.59,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We don't get paid till the job's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:26.54,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! What a bunch of louts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.54,0:04:27.83,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Speedwagon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:29.50,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look! There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:31.41,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.20,0:04:34.58,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Joestar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:37.50,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a joyous occasion!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:40.42,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Make a happy life for yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:47.18,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be here for you.\NIf you need me, I'll come running!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:50.81,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Though I might just get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:01.19,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Joestar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:04.57,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:23.87,Type,Default,0000,0000,0000,,-Atlantic Ocean, en route to America-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:37.31,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One bird all alone,\Nseparated from its flock?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:46.20,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Erina...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.20,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:54.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:57.41,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,These are tears of joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:59.58,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Because I am with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:06.09,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even back then, you strove \Nto be a true gentleman,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:09.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter the consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:14.52,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And now the proud\NJonathan Joestar is in my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:16.52,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:22.23,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When my heart was frozen in despair,\Nyou came and warmed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:28.15,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I am happy to have saved a world\Nwith you living in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:31.28,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wish Dad could've met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:34.99,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Erina, let's go and eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.19,0:06:35.79,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:42.63,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was about to tell you\Nto watch your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:53.05,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I hope today never ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:07:03.11,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, that's the engine room.\NIt sure fell into a filthy place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:07.99,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I could just sell it,\Nbut it makes me money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.96,0:07:11.03,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dear Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:15.49,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You sure do like picking on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:26.63,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't. I've never had alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:32.13,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Try a little. Just a sip.\NIt's not that strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.01,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Give it a taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:37.10,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:51.57,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:00.95,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:03.04,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.53,0:08:05.26,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:07.71,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dio is...alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.89,0:08:15.72,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Erina, go to our room and\Ndon't forget to lock the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:30.65,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this trunk?\NThe lock is open.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:37.03,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's funny.\NI can see a catch glinting inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:41.58,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That means...the trunk\Nis locked from the inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:49.34,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:51.59,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:56.43,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is my new body here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:58.31,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:02.43,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan is worried.\NThere's something wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:11.19,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo, look.\NSee what has become of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:16.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There is a reason\NI come before you in this state.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:20.58,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I show you my weakness?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:27.08,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Because, JoJo, though I once\Ndespised you, I now respect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:32.60,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I respect your courage,\Nyour spirit and your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.31,0:09:35.09,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I realize that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:36.34,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:37.84,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:40.55,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:43.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I never would\Nhave obtained the mask's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:48.97,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But because of you, the world\Nhas slipped from my grasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:53.82,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If there is a god who controls fate,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:57.61,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\NI am sure he bound ours the tightest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:03.33,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Our two existences are truly one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:09.17,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will take the body of \Nthe only man I respect
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.59,0:10:11.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and live in eternal glory!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.99,0:10:15.69,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That is the destiny laid out for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:20.18,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You will feel no pain,\Nthat is my last gift to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:23.47,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,His eyes...! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:27.35,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Live on as my body, JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:30.31,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:57.76,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,J-Jonathan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:11:00.87,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Eri...na...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.88,0:11:04.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:10.27,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you had just held still,\Nit would have been a painless death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:14.57,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Torn from your fairy tale into hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:19.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nunable to understand or even speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:26.04,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did JoJo never tell you of me,\Nthe mythical dweller in the dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:32.53,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I may not look like much, but surely\Nyou remember me, Erina Pendleton.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:36.80,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's Mrs. Erina Joestar now,\Nisn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:37.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:44.55,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The ship's full of monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:10.79,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As you ordered,\NI drained the life of one passenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:15.13,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And now most of the ship\Nhas joined our family!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:21.84,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And now we go to America.\NIsn't that right, Lord Dio?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:24.05,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:29.27,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:31.85,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Erina... Erina!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:35.48,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have to save...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:42.95,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't charge my Hamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:46.78,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Behold, Lord Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.34,0:12:51.20,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sniveling whelp can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:54.67,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He'll cause no mischief\Nwith Hamon now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:58.21,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is what he gets for \Ncrossing you, Lord Dio.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:00.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's time to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:06.51,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Or shall I just wait a few minutes\Nfor him to suffocate, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:08.93,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Wang Chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:11.18,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tolerate no insult to JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:16.08,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He is the man who brought me\Nto my current state.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:21.94,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Show him some respect by severing\Nhis head painlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.68,0:13:24.36,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Lord Dio.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:29.28,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And now my dear friend's body\Nwill become my future!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:30.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:38.67,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's up to something!\NStay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:42.21,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He might have one last trick\Nup his sleeve!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:47.89,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He can do nothing!\NSurely Lord Dio overestimates him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:54.22,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'll scoop out what little brains\Nyou have with my fingers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:57.85,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Must...save Erina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:14:03.36,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to use the last bit of Hamon\Nleft in my body all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:05.11,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A little will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:07.49,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look out, Wang Chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:22.00,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,S-Something broke inside of my body.\NSomething important.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:24.42,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:33.68,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This... This is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:36.05,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My last Hamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.05,0:14:40.60,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was too weak to destroy\Nthat zombie completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.93,0:14:43.11,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But it was enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:51.59,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:55.41,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo must have done something\Nto Wang Chan's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:15:00.67,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He disrupted its functions\Nwithout destroying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:04.67,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's made it cling tightly\Nto the machinery.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:08.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A-And the device it's clinging to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:12.18,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...is the paddle's screw shaft!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:15.93,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The strength of a zombie is enough\Nto stop the paddle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:21.94,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If the shaft stops, the steam inside\Nthe piston will keep building up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:24.94,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And after a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:26.94,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...the ship will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:30.40,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan, this can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:33.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How could this happen to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:36.80,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,R-Run, Erina.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:40.42,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The s-ship will explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:49.72,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know exactly what is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:55.62,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's too much for me.\NI don't know if I should cry or scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:59.70,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should just faint away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:03.73,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I can say one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:06.48,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Erina Joestar...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:10.32,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...will die with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:20.66,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In the warmth of these lips, alas,\NI feel the touch of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:23.62,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan Joestar is dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:28.50,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But we're together.\NI want to stay like this forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:34.34,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Until the ship explodes\Nand everything burns.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:37.34,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Until everything is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.11,0:17:00.66,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:06.46,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But you...have to keep living.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:09.71,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a storybook!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:14.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to save a baby and run?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.14,0:17:19.14,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To me, that heroism is cruelty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:23.48,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My only wish is to die with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:30.51,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That woman died to save her child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:34.24,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My mother did the same for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:39.26,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go with the baby. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.59,0:17:46.79,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You plan to destroy the whole ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:50.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo, you really never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:54.56,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But neither do I!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:58.29,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will live! No matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:18:00.90,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Along with your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:03.31,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Zombies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:09.61,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Devour Wang Chan's body\Nand restart the piston!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:17.11,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's starting to explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:29.25,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:34.14,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's already exploding!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.14,0:18:39.22,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have to protect myself\Nfrom the sun at all times!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:43.51,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So I am already prepared\Nin the event of an explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:51.11,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Erina, take a good look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:57.15,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now that JoJo can't use Hamon,\NI can safely steal his body!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:19:01.50,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then I will step into that trunk,\Nmy humble boudoir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:07.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That little shelter can withstand\Na blast made by a ton of dynamite!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:09.08,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come, JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:14.42,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And I bid you welcome,\Nmy new, eternal body!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:20.47,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:28.02,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dio...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:34.27,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Like you said, our fates might truly\Nbe one in the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:36.83,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I feel an odd warmth toward you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:40.74,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now our lives are bound completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:44.49,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And they will vanish\Nalong with this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.09,0:19:50.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fare...well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.17,0:19:52.00,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...Erina.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:20:00.42,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go, JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:03.22,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Release me!\NThink about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:05.97,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You'd like a shot at eternity, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:11.14,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can heal your wounds!\NYou can live forever with Erina, JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:13.23,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:18.98,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He... He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:21.96,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:32.50,Type,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan Joestar\NDied February 7, 1889
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:52.73,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan Joestar\Npassed away into oblivion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.57,0:21:00.53,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,His life was a piece of history\Ninvisible to ordinary people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:09.28,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They will never hear the tale\Nof his noble accomplishments.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:12.63,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But his descendants will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:23.88,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The new life that was inside me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:27.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nat that time will surely hear his story.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.93,0:21:36.44,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Erina Joestar was rescued\Nsoon after near the Canary Islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.97,0:21:41.31,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And the book of the stone mask\Nclosed for a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:47.57,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But this was only the beginning\Nof a new adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:51.31,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Part 1: Phantom Blood -- Fin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:38.56,Type,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.73,0:23:41.31,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was the fall of 1938.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:43.11,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to see you, Speedwagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.11,0:23:45.40,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know that, bastard?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.40,0:23:46.36,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.36,0:23:49.57,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Joseph Joestar.\NCall me JoJo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.57,0:23:51.81,Type,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chapter 10: JoJo in New York
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.81,0:23:53.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
